Caveats
- Create a new folder under the root to place new project 
- The folder ikeyit-foo is boilerplate code for a new project
- Refactor all "foo" symbols to the specified project name
- IMPORTANT: Strictly follow the folder ikeyit-foo to layout the new folder structure and write the code
- Set the project version to 1.0.0-SNAPSHOT and group to “com.ikeyit“ in gradle.properties
- Add includeBuild in the root [settings.gradle.kts](mdc:settings.gradle.kts) 
- Use gradle plugin "com.ikeyit.build-java-library" for library project
- Use gradle plugin "com.ikeyit.build-spring-boot" for spring boot project
- Use gradle plugin "com.ikeyit.build-grpc" for sdk project
- Always use yaml to define spring application properties